\c 82
\s Mwari ndiye mutongi mukuru
\d Pisarema raAsafi.
\p
\v 1 Mwari anomira paungano yaMwari; Anotonga pakati pavamwari.
\v 2 "Muchatonga zvisina kururama kusvikira riniko, Muchisanangura vanhu vakaipa?
\v 3 Tongerai mhaka dzavarombo nenherera;
\s Ruramisirai vanotambudzika navanoshaiwa chose.
\p
\v 4 Sunungurai varombo navashaiwi Varwirei paruoko rwowakaipa."
\p
\v 5 Havazivi, havanzwisisi; Vanofamba-famba murima; Nheyo dzose dzapasi
\s dzinozununguka.
\p
\v 6 Ndakati, "Muri vamwari,
\s Mose muri vanakomana
\s voWokumusorosoro.
\p
\v 7 Kunyange zvakadaro muchafa savanhu,
\p Muchafa somumwe wamachinda."
\v 8 Simukai Mwari, mutongere pasi; Nokuti ndudzi dzose dzichava
\s nhaka yenyu.
